reviewText: This is one of the worst movies I have ever seen.  It is not worth the tape it is made of. What is so SICK about this movie is that it is package in a cool and scary cover but the movie and I use the term loosely, is nothing but homemade porn.  I can't believe anyone ever thought that bad acting by trashy fools, ignorant plot, and shooting a movie with your mom's camera was ever a good idea.  This piece junk was as bad as the movie The Item.  Don't waste your time, money, or brain cells on these idiots that released this toilet water on anyone.  Could be decribed as cruel and unusal punishment.
